# Experimental 0.1

### changes from stable v0.5.9 (03.05.2024)

- Merged PR [#21](https://github.com/AndreyMrovol/LethalRichPresence/issues/21)
- improved project structure
- changed license to LGPL-3.0
- changed how placeholders are handled internally for improving performance
- added a config option to change update frequency
- added a dependency on MrovLib

# Experimental 0.2

- added a config option to hide `DiscordActivityUpdate` logs
- changed how placeholder resolving is logged: only on changes
- changed planet names
